{"tid":38631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大妓院】習近平是否會抓捕梁振英（上）","createTime":"2016-12-14T05:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T05:51:14.000Z","uid":48313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5883f572dab727118e4c1ada9f19ce320d1d465","tid":38631,"uid":48313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zk53siaf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzk53siaf&h=e6ec4403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁的突然宣佈退選印證了一個月前《大紀元時報》11月2日的獨家消息，即習近平當局對江派香港代理人梁振英態度明確，絕對不會讓其連任特首。消息說，「基本上是連任無望！不會給他連任，也不可能讓他連任。」當時消息還說，當局「不但不給他連任還要收拾他」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/D0JZNS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FD0JZNS&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=01b577f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/D0JZNS</a>"},{"pid":"317f9523c3f97e27fc19b34d424bb1fbce1f66b3","tid":38631,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"3bbf67fa0791f9102029d014125f9c7bc8ca1806","tid":38631,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}